1049:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_uart.c **** @verbatim
1050:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_uart.c ****  ===============================================================================
1051:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_uart.c ****                       ##### IO operation functions #####
